name: The Tezo Toad Observes
description: A seamless animated 20-second loop with atmospheric sounds. Made from some hand-drawn physical art and taken through digital processes. two teired prices: 5 x 1 tz, and 62 x 2 tezos ------  "The tezotoad patiently watches the tides of the crypto stream. His eyes track the flies that breed on fragments of broken blockchain. If only you could understand the mysteries contained in his song."
